                <fr:title text="Euler totient">Euler totient</fr:title>
                <fr:meta name="source">Dummit and Foote <fr:link href="/dummit-2004-abstract/" title="Abstract Algebra" uri="http://localhost:8000/dummit-2004-abstract/" display-uri="dummit-2004-abstract" type="local">Abstract Algebra</fr:link> Section 0.2</fr:meta>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>We have <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\varphi (n)]]></fr:tex> be the number of positive integers less than <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex> which are coprime to <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>,
<fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[\varphi (n)=|\{k\in \mathbb {N}\mid  k<n,\gcd (k,n)=1\}|.]]></fr:tex>
So <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\varphi (12)=|\{1,5,7,11\}|=4]]></fr:tex>, but <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\varphi (11)=10]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
              </fr:mainmatter>
